{"tid":266531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"警上門查偷拍裙底案 男子墜樓 身體斷成兩截","createTime":"2017-06-01T14:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T15:46:29.000Z","uid":3806,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b456098e262818ec70c17344f3284b82460cfc","tid":266531,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"沙田發生離奇墮樓案，下午4時許，一名男子由翠田街愉景花園一單位高處墮下，當場慘死，身體斷成兩截，死狀恐怖。消息指出，上周四(25日)一名女子報稱在辦公室內疑遭人偷拍裙底，黃大仙警區刑事調查隊今午到愉景花園一單位調查，其間警員尚未入屋，一名男子突然墮樓身亡。警方事後撿獲遺書，正調查案件原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc59cf5228953289ba8b997c054f59d35a21efdd","tid":266531,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"邊個咁無良心正評"},{"pid":"42543a1c7c8d9f83883b3e53feda336a0f0b15b2","tid":266531,"uid":25367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"係咪痴線，差佬變到可以隨意殺人"},{"pid":"e6f470246e5be2764356ec58975fedac46d0dd11","tid":266531,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪痴線，差佬變到可以隨意殺人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc15d0e1761c0cbde2e84f767b06af2bc0b75e6","tid":266531,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"瓏仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da428cba5a4d3f36bae42784b18d6cd0562b278","tid":266531,"uid":12348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"樓主開親J post都一定有圖，好彩今次冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n